race.comment: FROSE (7) is a seasoned mare with a strong record at the trip and a great record with claimer Waller aboard. Just missed fresh and has placed only try here. Will take catching again. CLOSE TO MIDNIGHT (1) gave a sight in far tougher company off a long break but weakened late. Will be much fitter and looks very well placed here to find form. COOL CHARLIE (8) doesn't win out of turn but expecting a strong run fresh. Fitter for two jump-outs, has good early speed and drawn to lead.  NO OVERTAKING (4) is another speedy type resuming. Got off the mark at last run of a three start campaign and returns here on the back of two good jump-outs. Tricky gate but will be in this for a long way.
